":"维多利亚州位于澳大利亚东南部，坐拥由南大洋雕琢而成的绵延千余英里的海岸线。从高空俯瞰，这里的海滩宛如一条条宽阔的浅色沙带，边缘环绕着碧绿的海水与崎岖的峭壁。这种海陆交融的独特景致构成了该地区的主要魅力所在。著名的“大洋路”沿这段海岸线蜿蜒延伸约150英里，途经热门冲浪胜地、林木葱郁的海角以及各具特色的海滨小镇。","Image":{"Url":"https://ts1.tc.mm.bing.net/th?id=OHR.VictoriaBeach_ZH-CN8892195426_1920x1080.webp","Wallpaper":"/th?id=OHR.VictoriaBeach_ZH-CN8892195426_1920x1200.jpg\u0026rf=LaDigue_1920x1200.jpg","Downloadable":true},"Headline":"陆地与海洋的鸟瞰图","Title":"陆地与海洋的鸟瞰图，维多利亚州，澳大利亚","Copyright":"© Nearmap/Getty Images","SocialGood":null,"MapLink":{"Url":"","Link":""},"QuickFact":{"MainText":"十二使徒岩一直在发生变化；在2005年发生一次重大坍塌后，最初的石灰岩柱目前仅存八座。","LinkUrl":"","LinkText":""},"TriviaUrl":"/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz\u0026filters=WQOskey:\u0022HPQuiz_20260710_VictoriaBeach\u0022\u0026FORM=HPQUIZ","BackstageUrl":"/search?q=%e6%be%b3%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%a9%e4%ba%9a%e7%bb%b4%e5%a4%9a%e5%88%a9%e4%ba%9a%e5%b7%9e\u0026form=hpcapt\u0026filters=HpDate:\u002220260709_1600\u0022+mgzv3configlist:\u0022BingQA_Encyclopedia_Layout\u0022","TriviaId":"HPQuiz_20260710_VictoriaBeach"},"Ssd":"20260710","Name":"VictoriaBeach","Market":"ZH-CN","Hash":"8892195426","FullDateString":"2026 7月 10"}],"PreloadMediaContents":[],"LocStrings":{"LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_IOTD":"每日一图","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_IOTD_LEARN_MORE":"了解更多","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_DONATE_NOW":"立即捐赠","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_FACT":"速览:","LOC_HOMEPAGE_GALLERY_CARD_TITLE":"近期的主页图片","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_GALLERY_IMAGE_ARIALABEL":"{0} 的主页图像","LOC_HOMEPAGE_ON_THIS_DAY_TITLE":"历史上的今天","LOC_HOMEPAGE_ON_THIS_DAY_IMAGE_ARIALABEL":"在这一天，在 {0}中，{1}","LOC_HOMEPAGE_SHARE_TOOLTIP":"共享今日必应主页","LOC_HOMEPAGE_WALLPAPERDOWNLOAD_TOOLTIP":"下载今日美图。仅限用作桌面壁纸。","LOC_MUSCARD_DOWNLOAD_LINK":"下载此图像","LOC_HOMEPAGE_WALLPAPERNOTAVAILABLE":"此图片不能下载用作壁纸。","LOC_HOMEPAGE_INFO_TEXT":"信息","LOC_BING_WP_APP_LINK":"https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2127455","LOC_BING_WP_APP_LINK_TEXT":"获取新版必应壁纸应用","LOC_BING_APP_TEXT":"在设备上获取必应壁纸","LOC_BING_APP_LINK_PC":"https://bing.microsoftapp.net/bing/?adjust=nk9xr